networking_key1: Do log ko mil kar sabse pehle yeh videos dekhni hai
networking_key2: Ab aapko 30 mins ke liye aapas mei `english` mei baat karni hai.
networking_key3: Baat karte karte, aap observe karein, ki aap kitne tech words use kar paa rahe hai.
networking_key4: Aur agar aapka partner koi aisa tech word bolta hai, jo aapko nahi pata, ya aap generally use nahi kartein. Inn words ko bhi samajhne ki phir koshish karein.
networking_key5: Iss discussion ko karte hue, aap inn points ke baarein mei bhi soch sakte hai:
networking_key6: `Networking` kya hota hai?, isse aapko kya samajh mai aaya?
networking_key7: Aapke `internet` shabdh sunte hi kya dimag mai aata hai?
networking_key8: Aap aapne phone se laptop ke beech mai kya ek network bna sakte ho kaise?
networking_key9: Same network pe hona or different network pe hona ka kya matlab hai?
networking_key10: IP address kya hota hai?, IP address ki kya zarurat hoti hai?
networking_key11: IP address real life mai kis cheez ka replacement hai?
networking_key12: Ek computer jo ki aapke local computer pe nahi hai, aap usse kaise baat karenge?
networking_key13: Upar waale process, mai kya DNS ka use aayega?
networking_key14: Make a list ki aur kya kya naye tech shabdh hai, jinka aapne naam suna.
